{{External|rs|rsc=Crossbow bolts}}
'''Bolts''' are the ammunition used by [[crossbow (weapon)|crossbow]]s. Most types of bolts are made using a combination of the [[Smithing]] and [[Fletching]] skills; the metal component is made with Smithing, and [[feathers]] are added with Fletching. Certain special bolts can only be obtained through other methods, such as [[monster drops]] or [[specialist shop]]s.

Different types of bolts can be stored in a [[bolt pouch]] to conserve space. Like other [[Ranged]] ammunition, bolts can occasionally be left on the ground after firing, able to be picked up by the player.

==Types of bolts==
===Normal metal bolts===
All of the following bolts can be made through the Smithing and Fletching skills, excluding dragon; the unfinished bolts are obtained as a monster drop, and can be finished using [[feather]]s. All metal bolts can be [[poisoned]].

