===Other player-made bolts===
[[Silver bolts]] are much like other silver items, in that they are [[Crafting|crafted]] using an appropriate [[bolt mould|mould]] and a [[furnace]]. Silver bolts are the only [[ranged weapons]] that can be used effectively against [[vampyre]]s.
